Class FractionImpl

java.lang.Object
FractionImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Fraction, Comparable<Fraction>
public class FractionImpl extends Object implements Fraction
FractionImpl implements the Fraction interface, representing a rational number. It ensures the fraction is always stored in its simplest form with a positive denominator.
